edu.cnm.deepdive.mealplanit.model

Class Plan

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.mealplanit.model.Plan

  • public class Plan
extends Object
    Model that holds the information for the Plan table when it is created in the database. A user can have multiple plans and are connected by having an id for both Person and Diet.
